This theme does NOT redistribute Scout brand imagery or logos. Scout-branded
section logos (Beavers, Cubs, Scouts, Explorers, Network) and the fleur-de-lis
must be downloaded directly from https://scoutsbrand.org.uk by each Scout
Group using this theme.

The Scout brand, logos, and trade marks are © The Scout Association and are
provided by them under their own brand-asset terms. Nothing in this theme's
licence affects those rights.

The colour palette presets in data/palettes.toml use hex values published in
the Scouts Brand Guidelines (Our Colours, 2023). Hex codes are factual data
and are not themselves copyrightable.

The "Inter Tight" typeface is loaded at runtime from Google Fonts under the
SIL Open Font License 1.1.
